      "title": "Harmonic functions starlike in the unit disk",
      "abstract": "Abstract Complex-valued harmonic functions that are univalent and sense-preserving in the unit disk Δ can be written in the form f = h + ḡ, where h and g are analytic in Δ. We give univalence criteria and sufficient coefficient conditions for normalized harmonic functions that are starlike of order α, 0 ≤ α"
